• If you fail to hit the target, the grapple attempt fails.

Step Three: (Hold)
• Make an opposed grapple check as a free action:
  Attacker [[ 1d20 + [[@{grapple}]][Grapple Check Modifier] ]] > [[ 1d20 + [[ [[1-?{Target Type (Ask GM)|PC,0|NPC,1}]]*[[@{target|grapple}]] + ?{Target Type (Ask GM)|PC,0|NPC,1}*[[@{target|npcgrapple}]] ]][Grapple Check Modifier] ]] Defender
